abstract: Antiwar rally in eastern Ukrainian city of Donetsk is unusual in that protesters call for withdrawal of both Ukrainian Army and Russian-backed separatists.
lead_paragraph: About 500 protesters in Donetsk called on both the Ukrainian and the separatist leadership to stop the fighting.

headline.main: Discontent in Eastern Ukraine Leads to Rare Public Protest
headline.print_headline: Rally Scorns Both Sides in Rebel Area of Ukraine

snippet: About 500 protesters in Donetsk called on both the Ukrainian and the separatist leadership to stop the fighting.
